<div title="TodayMacro" modifier="JeremyRuston" created="200510302315" tags="macros">
<pre>The {{{&lt;&lt;today&gt;&gt;}}} macro inserts the current date and time into a tiddler. It's updated each time the tiddler is redisplayed.

It can optionally take a DateFormatString to determine the way that the date is displayed:

{{{
&lt;&lt;today&gt;&gt;
&lt;&lt;today&gt;&gt;
}}}

Results in:
&lt;&lt;today&gt;&gt;
&lt;&lt;today&gt;&gt;</pre>
</div>
